{
  "text": "The structure of this alkaline degradant was elucidated using spectroscopic techniques like MASS, NMR and IR spectroscopy. The degradant was identified as 5-(4-fluorophenyl)-2-[(4-fluorophenyl amino)-(4-hydroxyphenyl) methyl]-pent-4-enoic acid (Fig. 4) [CITATION_1] . ",
